    "description": "<p>This barbarian has a deep connection to an elemental plane and can manifest that element when raging. At the start of their Rage choose one Element and you gain benefits depending on the chosen element which lasts until the end of the battle.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Fire</strong>: Enemies within 3m recieve fire damage equal to their current Rage. <strong>AURA</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Earth</strong>: Friendly creatures within 3m recieve <strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">THP</span></strong> equal to their current Rage. <strong>AURA</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Water</strong>: Enemies within 3m have their <strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">MP</span></strong> reduced equal to their Rage, however not lower than 2 <strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">MP</span></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Air</strong>: Friendly creatures 3m gain <strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">MP</span></strong> equal to half their current Rage. Additionally their long jump distance is increased by a number of meters equal to their rage and the high jump by half their rage. <strong>AURA</strong></p></li></ul>",
